</div>
</li>
<li>
<div class="flagDesc">
<ul class="flagDesc">
<li class="flagName"><a name="user_F-mavx" id="user_F-mavx">-mavx</a></li>
<li class="flagDescRE"><span class="tt">(?:^|(?&lt;=\s))-mavx(?:\([^\)]+\))?(?:=\S*)?(?=\s|$)</span></li>
<li class="descText">
