   </p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</li>
<li>
<div class="flagDesc">
<ul class="flagDesc">
<li class="flagName"><a name="user_F-mfmaf" id="user_F-mfmaf">-mfmaf</a></li>
<li class="flagDescRE"><span class="tt">(?:^|(?&lt;=\s))-mfmaf(?:\([^\)]+\))?(?:=\S*)?(?=\s|$)</span></li>
<li class="descText">
<p>
      Generate code to take advantage of fused multiply-add
   </p>
</li>
